question: What restaurant can I find as I progress towards the Potted Plant Inc., Scottsdale, AZ from American Institute of Dental Assisting, Gilbert, AZ, within a radius of 100 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-111.688039 33.367907)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-111.920729 33.631545)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-111.688039 33.367907)',4326)::geography, 100000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-111.688039 33.367907)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
